    <script>
        /**
         * Checking for asia browser
         * [isFirefox description]
         * @type {String}
         */
        (function () {

            var isChromiumBased = "WebkitAppearance" in document.documentElement.style,
                asiaLocales = ["zh", "zh-CN", "zh-HK", "ja", "ko"],
                asiaLength = asiaLocales.length;

            for (var langIndex = 0; langIndex < asiaLength; langIndex++) {
                if (asiaLocales[langIndex] === navigator.language && isChromiumBased) {
                    document.getElementsByTagName("html")[0].className += " asia-browser";
                }
            }
        })();
    </script>
